<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ainote.az</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#1c1c1e">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="ainote.az">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- READ PROGRESS BAR (post pages only) -->
    <div class="read-progress-bar" id="readProgressBar"></div>

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header class="site-header">
        <div class="container header-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo">ainote<span>.az</span></a>
            <div class="header-right">
                <button class="hdr-icon-btn" id="coffeeBtn" aria-label="Günün Xəbərləri" title="Günün Xəbərləri">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
                </button>
                <button class="hdr-icon-btn" id="statsBtn" aria-label="AI Statistika" title="AI Statistika">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/><line x1="2" y1="20" x2="22" y2="20"/></svg>
                </button>
                <button class="hdr-icon-btn" id="toolsBtn" aria-label="AI Tools" title="AI Tools">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/><polyline points="7 10 10 13 17 8"/></svg>
                </button>
                <!-- Dark/Light mode toggle -->
                <button class="hdr-icon-btn" id="themeToggleBtn" aria-label="Tema dəyiş" title="Tema dəyiş">
                    <svg class="icon-moon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/></svg>
                    <svg class="icon-sun" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"/><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"/></svg>
                </button>
                <button class="hdr-icon-btn" id="searchToggleBtn" aria-label="Axtar" title="Axtar">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"></line></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="search-bar-wrap" id="searchBarWrap">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="search-bar-inner">
                    <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Xəbərlərdə axtar..." autocomplete="off" />
                    <button id="searchSubmitBtn"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="18" height="18"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg></button>
                    <button id="searchCloseBtn" aria-label="Bağla"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="18" height="18"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></button>
                </div>
                <div class="search-results" id="searchResults"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- GÜNÜN XƏBƏRLƏRİ PANEL -->
    <div class="side-overlay" id="coffeeOverlay">
        <div class="side-panel" id="coffeePanel">
            <div class="coffee-bg-img" id="coffeeBgImg"></div>
            <div class="side-panel-header">
                <div class="side-panel-logo">
                    <div class="cp-logo-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="26" height="26"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg></div>
                    <div class="cp-logo-box">
                        <div class="cp-site-name">ainote<span>.az</span></div>
                        <div class="cp-panel-label">Günün Xəbərləri</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-date-block">
                    <span class="panel-day-num" id="panelDayNum">8</span>
                    <span class="panel-month-year"><em id="panelMonth">MART</em><span id="panelYear">2026</span></span>
                </div>
                <button class="side-panel-close" id="coffeeClose"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="16" height="16"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></button>
            </div>
            <div class="side-panel-body">
                <div class="coffee-news-list" id="coffeeNewsList"><div class="panel-loading"><div class="panel-spinner"></div><span>Yüklənir...</span></div></div>
                <div class="coffee-footer-tag">#ainoteKahveniz</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI STATİSTİKA PANEL -->
    <div class="side-overlay" id="statsOverlay">
        <div class="side-panel" id="statsPanel">
            <div class="side-panel-header">
                <div class="side-panel-logo"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="24" height="24"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/><line x1="2" y1="20" x2="22" y2="20"/></svg><span>AI Statistika</span></div>
                <button class="side-panel-close" id="statsClose"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="18" height="18"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></button>
            </div>
            <div class="side-panel-body stats-body">
                <p class="stats-subtitle">2025–2026 · Süni İntellekt Məlumatları</p>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">$632B</div><div class="stat-label">Qlobal AI bazarının dəyəri (2028 proqnozu)</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:78%"></div></div></div>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">700M+</div><div class="stat-label">ChatGPT aylıq aktiv istifadəçi sayı</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:92%"></div></div></div>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">85%</div><div class="stat-label">Şirkətlərin AI-ı iş proseslərinə inteqrasiya nisbəti</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:85%"></div></div></div>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">97M</div><div class="stat-label">2025-ci ildə AI sahəsindəki iş yeri sayı (qlobal)</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:60%"></div></div></div>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">4.4T$</div><div class="stat-label">AI-ın qlobal iqtisadiyyata illik töhfəsi (McKinsey)</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:70%"></div></div></div>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">40%</div><div class="stat-label">Dünya işlərinin AI tərəfindən avtomatlaşdırılma potensialı</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:40%"></div></div></div>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">3,500+</div><div class="stat-label">Mövcud AI alət və platformaların sayı</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
                <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">$200B</div><div class="stat-label">2025-ci ildə qlobal AI investisiya həcmi</div><div class="stat-bar"><div class="stat-bar-fill" style="width:65%"></div></div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI TOOLS PANEL -->
    <div class="side-overlay" id="toolsOverlay">
        <div class="side-panel" id="toolsPanel">
            <div class="side-panel-header">
                <div class="side-panel-logo"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="24" height="24"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/><polyline points="7 10 10 13 17 8"/></svg><span>AI Tools</span></div>
                <button class="side-panel-close" id="toolsClose"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="18" height="18"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></button>
            </div>
            <div class="side-panel-body">
                <p class="stats-subtitle">Ən çox istifadə edilən AI alətlər</p>
                <div class="tools-grid">
